# DockerAgent Bitwarden-backed environment template
#
# This file is now mostly documentation. The actual values come from Bitwarden.
#
# Preferred flow:
#   1) Store all values in Bitwarden item: DockerAgent Credentials
#      - Custom fields: GITHUB_TOKEN, AZDO_TOKEN (hidden)
#      - Custom fields: DOCKER_REGISTRY, GITHUB_ORG, GITHUB_RUNNER_NAME, etc. (text)
#   2) Unlock bw locally: bw unlock && export BW_SESSION="..."
#   3) Run: ./render-env-from-bitwarden.sh
#   4) Deploy: docker stack deploy -c docker-compose.yml docker-agents
#
# The rendered file is .env.runtime (gitignored).

# Bitwarden item ID for DockerAgent Credentials
BW_DOCKERAGENT_ITEM_ID=80186610-10ab-4eb5-a2ce-b40b005178eb

# Override the generated env file path if needed
DOCKERAGENT_ENV_FILE=.env.runtime

# ============================================
# Values stored in Bitwarden: DockerAgent Credentials
# ============================================
# GITHUB_TOKEN (hidden)
# AZDO_TOKEN (hidden)
# DOCKER_REGISTRY
# GITHUB_ORG
# GITHUB_RUNNER_NAME
# GITHUB_RUNNER_LABELS
# AZDO_ORG_URL
# AZDO_POOL
# AZDO_AGENT_NAME
# VERSION
# TZ